        Redirects to a given URL with the parameters specified in a Map
        Parameters:
        url - The URL to redirect to as a String
        parameters - Parameters to be included at the end of the URL as a HTTP GET. This is a map whose entries are written out as key1=value1&key2=value2 etc..
